1
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,719
Grandpa

2
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,159
Grandpa

3
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:05,159
Grandpa, wake up, Grandpa.

4
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,519
You promised me.

5
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,959
Grandpa!

6
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:37,680
It was the Xieling Sect that harmed your family.

7
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,319
Take your revenge on the right person.

8
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,400
If you want revenge,

9
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,079
make sure you don't find the wrong people.

10
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,079
What Xieling Sect?

11
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,359
It's just a nice-sounding name.

12
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:47,760
Aren't you all just thieves?

13
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,000
So,

14
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:52,239
you're not going to let us go?

15
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:56,680
Who let us go thirty years ago?

16
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,439
Listen.

17
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:29,960
Look.

18
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,039
It's these hornets again.

19
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,560
Moving in an orderly way.

20
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,840
They must have been specially tamed.

21
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,039
Fatty,

22
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,280
come with me to help Senior Master.

23
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:44,759
Let's go.

24
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,439
Wait.

25
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,039
There are so many hornets.

26
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,680
Aren't you just going to your deaths?

27
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,840
Ding Dawei,

28
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,039
where is your insect lure?

29
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,879
Insect lure, insect lure...

30
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,840
I say, sister,

31
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,560
people keep pets for fun.

32
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,479
But you,

33
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,560
keeping a bunch of big bees

34
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,840
just to harm people for fun?

35
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,680
Perfect timing.

36
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,680
Saves me the trouble of dealing with you one by one.

37
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,479
She's blocking us and doesn't want us to pass.

38
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,360
Which means

39
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,439
the tomb of the Dian King

40
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:41,240
is right inside the Heavenly Gate behind these stairs.

41
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,039
I'll count to three,

42
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,240
and we'll charge forward together.

43
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:47,080
I'll cover the rear. One, two, three!

44
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,280
Go!

45
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,400
Go!

46
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,639
Senior Master!

47
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,560
Senior Master! Senior Master!

48
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,160
Senior Master!

49
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,319
Senior Master!

50
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,040
Lao Lu,

51
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,959
go up first and see if the Heavenly Gate can be opened.

52
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:41,879
Open, open, open...

53
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:42,839
Give me the insect lure.

54
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,879
Go up with your Teacher Lu.

55
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:44,480
Protect him well.

56
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,240
Okay, okay. Lao Lu!

57
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:45,959
Hurry!

58
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,240
Okay, okay. Let's go.

59
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,879
Shutong, take good care of Senior Master.

60
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:16,399
Senior Master, let me bandage you up.

61
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:48,439
Fatty, is your stamina up for this?

62
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,199
Cut the crap.

63
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,759
Teacher Lu,

64
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,000
there's no way here.

65
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,560
Go, go, go.

66
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,040
Go, hurry!

67
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,279
Hurry up!

68
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:08,319
Hurry up!

69
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,279
Finally here.

70
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,319
Apprentice,

71
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:32,480
we can't be too gentle with this.

72
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,920
We have to learn from the big fatty.

73
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,879
I understand.

74
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:36,680
Be savage.

75
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,600
One, two, three, go!

76
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:47,000
Apprentice, how is it?

77
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:48,680
Are you okay? Did you hit your head?

78
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,120
A bit dizzy. Dizzy.

79
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,800
Fatty!

80
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,800
This thing can move.

81
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,680
A... a mechanism!

82
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:19,399
Little punk, trying this on me?

83
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,720
Huarong Dao.

84
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,680
What is it?

85
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,040
You don't even know Huarong Dao?

86
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,800
In the late Eastern Han Dynasty, the world was in chaos.

87
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,800
The empire, long divided, must unite; long united, divide.

88
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,360
The eight warlords...

89
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,399
Teacher Lu, Teacher Lu, you're getting off-topic.

90
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,360
This, this...

91
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,080
Right, right.

92
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,480
This thing,

93
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,679
it's just a puzzle game.

94
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,480
As long as we put these boards

95
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,679
together into the right pattern,

96
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,440
and this pattern

97
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:43,279
is the key to opening the door.

98
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:00,799
Not this again.

99
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,000
No.

100
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,440
It seems a bit different this time.

101
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,519
What could be different?

102
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,840
More and more hornets are gathering.

103
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,519
She's trying to

104
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,600
gather all the hornets in Guyu here.

105
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,840
If this goes on,

106
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,200
just the few of us

107
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,080
won't be able to hold them off.

108
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,559
It all depends on Lao Lu now.

109
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,399
I wonder if the Heavenly Gate can be opened.

110
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:47,919
This...

111
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,679
Quick, quick, get out of the way!

112
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:19,080
Don't get hit when the door opens!

113
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,840
Don't get hit!

114
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,879
Do you know this character?

115
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,600
Yes, it's Jing.

116
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:24,559
Brilliant, right?

117
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,080
Just wait.

118
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,679
Lao Lu is an intellectual.

119
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,240
He's fine with reading characters,

120
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,320
but asking him to open a mechanism

121
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,399
is just making things difficult for him.

122
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,240
Yeah.

123
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,080
Old Chen,

124
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,240
we still have to rely on you for this.

125
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,480
Lao Lu is unreliable.

126
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:36,919
What are you hesitating for?

127
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,360
We've got Senior Master covered.

128
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,080
Go quickly!

129
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,480
Okay.

130
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,360
Hurry up and go!

131
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,120
Staff Officer He, take Senior Master and go first.

132
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,039
I'll give her a little gift.

133
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:58,960
Be careful!

134
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:11,799
Lao Lu!

135
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:13,559
Brother!

136
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:15,480
Brother!

137
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,240
Lao Lu, how is it?

138
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:20,000
We just found a couplet.

139
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,600
And then?

140
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,440
Mr. Lu figured out it's the character Jing.

141
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:25,039
But the door just won't open!

142
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:28,080
Why must scholars make things hard for scholars?

143
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:32,320
My talents are unappreciated!

144
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:32,879
Lao Lu!

145
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:33,600
Heavens.

146
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:34,840
Your idea isn't wrong.

147
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,879
Did you miss something?

148
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:37,120
I didn't miss anything!

149
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,639
Look.

150
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:39,240
Two shapes in one body.

151
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,559
One two, two twos.

152
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,440
Four branches and eight heads.

153
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,840
Isn't this just a Jing?

154
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,759
Then flying spring flows upward.

155
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:48,519
Water comes out of the well to drink.

156
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,519
What's that up there?

157
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,919
Which one?

158
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,440
Head resides in one room.

159
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:56,919
What does that mean?

160
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:58,639
Why should I care what it means?

161
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:00,399
I've already pieced together the Jing.

162
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:02,720
Let it reside in however many rooms it wants! This...

163
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,600
It...

164
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,159
Old Chen,

165
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,879
I might really be wrong.

166
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,759
I missed a little dot.

167
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,279
What little dot?

168
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,720
In Large Seal Script,

169
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:20,480
the character Jing is

170
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:24,639
two horizontal and two vertical lines with a dot in the middle.

171
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,639
There's no dot!

172
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,639
How was I supposed to know?

173
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,240
That's why I say they're hooligans!

174
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:39,799
They didn't give a dot!

175
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:53,480
Leg!

176
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,440
Have you opened it yet?

177
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,080
Sister!

178
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,639
Go, quickly!

179
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:04,200
Find the dot! Find the dot!

180
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,279
Hurry and find the dot!

181
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:13,759
It's open!

182
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,080
The giant hornets are coming! Hurry!

183
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,840
It's open! It's open!

184
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,320
Come on, let's go!

185
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:30,200
Hurry! Quick, quick!

186
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,519
Hurry! They're catching up!

187
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:44,399
Hurry up, Fatty!

188
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:50,919
Hurry, let's go!

189
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,240
Senior Master, let me!

190
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,320
Remember.

191
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,000
Senior Master!

192
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:04,360
If you get trapped in a maze,

193
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,440
try looking to the sky.

194
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,159
Senior Master!

195
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:14,879
Senior Master!

196
00:14:15,799 --> 00:14:17,200
Senior Master!

197
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,919
Senior Master!

198
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,080
Chen Youxi!

199
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,759
This is as far as I can go with you.

200
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:42,039
You must find the Lingxiao Pearl.

201
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:49,279
Being able to join you on this journey,

202
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,679
I can die without regrets.
